| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Peer-led vs. Manager-led** | Strongly favours peer-led; 88% vs. 50% peer influence gap (Microsoft Research, 2026) | Leaders still contribute through modelling, not mandating |
| **Opt-in vs. Mandatory** | Favours opt-in for sharing; mandatory risks performative content and psychological reactance | Consumption must be frictionless to overcome self-selection barrier |
